<header class="jumbotron mb-0">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to The Broumvirate</h1>
        <p class="lead">We get the senior discount at Taco Bell</p>
    </div>
</header>

<div
    id="carouselFrontPage"
    class="carousel slide m-0 pt-4 pb-2"
    data-ride="carousel"
>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-inner m-0">
            <div class="carousel-item active my-2">
                <h4>"Nothing was happening but you were all laughing."</h4>
                <p class="bm-carousel-q">- Anna F.</p>
                <p></p>
            </div>

            <div class="carousel-item my-2">
                <h4>"Will you guys take a picture with my daughter?"</h4>
                <p class="bm-carousel-q">- Some Rando</p>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item my-2">
                <h4>
                    "I was with you guys for 30 seconds and I already wanted to
                    cry."
                </h4>
                <p class="bm-carousel-q">- Anna F.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item my-2">
                <h4>"Elton John would be better if his name was Alden."</h4>
                <p class="bm-carousel-q">- Alden</p>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item my-2">
                <h4>
                    "Ah yes, my least favourite friend group: Ben's friends."
                </h4>
                <p class="bm-carousel-q">- Dream Megan</p>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item my-2">
                <h4>
                    "THIS IS INCREDIBLE! This is exactly the kind of content I
                    hope for on the internet."
                </h4>
                <p class="bm-carousel-q">- Siobhan Flanagan</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a
        class="carousel-control-prev"
        href="#carouselFrontPage"
        role="button"
        data-slide="prev"
    >
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a
        class="carousel-control-next"
        href="#carouselFrontPage"
        role="button"
        data-slide="next"
    >
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row d-flex justify-content-around">
        <div class="card col-md-5 p-0 m-3">
            <img
                class="card-img-top mx-0 bm-f-card-top"
                src="/img/gbs.jpg"
                alt="Card image cap"
            />
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Watch GBS!</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    What drinks they find you'll never know, that's why you
                    watch the Generally Bad Show!
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCUSu-jMpoqqiTv3sOA9fSgA"
                    class="btn btn-primary"
                    >Visit our Youtube</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card col-md-5 p-0 m-3">
            <img
                class="card-img-top mx-0 bm-f-card-top"
                src="/img/artemisbanner.jpg"
                alt="Card image cap"
            />
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Artemis Fowl Remake</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    We've gone viral in the Artemis Fowl fandom! Check out our
                    shot for shot remake of the movie.
                </p>
                <a
                    href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EMGa53miavE"
                    class="btn btn-primary"
                    >Watch Now</a
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

